Field Required Type Description
main_text required string Contains the main text of a prediction, usually the name of the place.
main_text_matched_substrings required Array<PlaceAutocompleteMatchedSubstring> Contains an array with offset value and length. These describe the location of the entered term in the prediction result text, so that the term can be highlighted if desired.See PlaceAutocompleteMatchedSubstring for more information.
secondary_text required string Contains the secondary text of a prediction, usually the location of the place.
secondary_text_matched_substrings optional Array<PlaceAutocompleteMatchedSubstring> Contains an array with offset value and length. These describe the location of the entered term in the prediction result text, so that the term can be highlighted if desired.See PlaceAutocompleteMatchedSubstring for more information.
